WEBVTT

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:43.560
Xishi, Sister Wu

00:00:44.039 --> 00:00:45.000
Just an auntie

00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:47.200
I've seen the puzzle online

00:00:47.719 --> 00:00:48.560
It's very interesting

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:49.479
It's just that...

00:00:49.600 --> 00:00:50.799
I don't know your true strength

00:00:51.079 --> 00:00:51.880
How about a game?

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:53.280
What a pity

00:00:53.320 --> 00:00:54.159
I don't know how to play

00:00:54.520 --> 00:00:55.000
What?

00:00:56.039 --> 00:00:56.799
Boss Nan

00:00:57.119 --> 00:00:58.640
I know you want a gimmick

00:00:59.320 --> 00:01:01.640
But bringing an auntie from the market

00:01:01.719 --> 00:01:03.840
Isn't that a bit insulting to us?

00:01:04.040 --> 00:01:04.599
Exactly

00:01:05.319 --> 00:01:05.920
Boss Nan

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:07.879
I have a reputation to uphold

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:08.920
Forgive me

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:10.000
But I can't play along

00:01:13.319 --> 00:01:14.319
You...

00:01:15.879 --> 00:01:17.000
Have you forgotten

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:18.640
just what

00:01:19.359 --> 00:01:20.680
your status is?

00:01:22.159 --> 00:01:23.560
I can make you

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:25.560
And I can destroy you

00:01:26.359 --> 00:01:27.239
Understand?

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:37.079
This match

00:01:37.719 --> 00:01:39.040
You are only allowed to win

00:01:39.599 --> 00:01:40.519
You must not lose

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:44.640
Xishi, Sister Wu

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:45.760
Ball Boy Wei He

00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:46.319
Where is he?

00:01:46.480 --> 00:01:47.040
Oh

00:01:47.040 --> 00:01:47.920
He's doing his homework

00:02:06.359 --> 00:02:06.879
Kid

00:02:07.519 --> 00:02:08.479
You like playing billiards too?

00:02:08.840 --> 00:02:09.240
Yeah

00:02:13.039 --> 00:02:13.639
Want to learn?

00:02:14.400 --> 00:02:15.080
I'll teach you

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:16.680
Thanks, big brother

00:02:17.879 --> 00:02:18.520
Kid

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.759
Do you know the rules of Snooker?

00:02:21.000 --> 00:02:21.360
I do

00:02:21.400 --> 00:02:22.479
Of course I do

00:02:32.919 --> 00:02:33.680
Kid

00:02:34.159 --> 00:02:35.360
The rules of Snooker

00:02:35.360 --> 00:02:37.240
are that you must hit a red ball first

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.280
before hitting a colored ball

00:02:38.639 --> 00:02:39.080
Do you know that?

00:02:39.479 --> 00:02:40.280
I know

00:02:41.039 --> 00:02:41.639
But

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:43.879
your Left Wheel Whirlwind obstacle is set so well

00:02:44.159 --> 00:02:45.319
how can I hit a red ball?

00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:48.639
What did you say?

00:02:49.039 --> 00:02:50.439
Left Wheel Whirlwind

00:02:50.599 --> 00:02:51.840
One of the Six Heavenly Forms

00:02:51.960 --> 00:02:53.039
You play pretty well

00:02:55.879 --> 00:02:56.960
Who are you?

00:02:59.240 --> 00:03:01.439
My master is Lao Gui

00:03:03.199 --> 00:03:03.759
Oh

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:04.919
Shh

00:03:05.319 --> 00:03:06.280
See you later

00:03:07.319 --> 00:03:08.120
See you later

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:16.080
Who is that kid?

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:18.680
Ball Boy Wei He

00:03:18.800 --> 00:03:20.080
Ball Boy Wei He is...

00:03:22.639 --> 00:03:23.919
Puzzle Dragon's...

00:03:24.080 --> 00:03:26.360
Ball Boy Wei He is a kid

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.319
Hei Ba

00:03:57.800 --> 00:03:58.840
How did you get interested

00:03:59.120 --> 00:04:00.360
in joining the challenge match?

00:04:00.639 --> 00:04:01.960
Why are you everywhere?

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:05.520
Hei Ba is a contestant from our Chaoli Group

00:04:06.199 --> 00:04:07.639
What right do you have to question his eligibility?

00:04:08.599 --> 00:04:10.120
How many invitation letters do you want?

00:04:10.280 --> 00:04:11.439
I'll write them for you

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:12.599
How could I?

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:14.719
The heiress of Chaoli Group is here

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:17.000
How would I dare question Hei Ba's eligibility?

00:04:17.680 --> 00:04:18.839
I'm just worried

00:04:19.279 --> 00:04:20.720
that he'll lose too miserably

00:04:21.399 --> 00:04:23.000
and shame your Chaoli Group

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:24.639
You should worry about yourself

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:25.959
Hei Ba

00:04:27.519 --> 00:04:29.720
Five Little Dragons of the East Challenge

00:04:30.519 --> 00:04:32.000
Which one do you want to challenge?

00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:37.439
I want to play all five

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:40.120
What?

00:04:42.040 --> 00:04:43.920
I said I want to play all five

00:04:44.560 --> 00:04:45.680
Did I hear that right?

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:47.199
These Five Little Dragons of the East...

00:04:47.399 --> 00:04:48.079
I heard that

00:04:48.560 --> 00:04:50.000
every one of them is naturally gifted

00:04:50.120 --> 00:04:50.920
with unique skills

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:52.600
Is Hei Ba that arrogant?

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:54.279
He's too arrogant

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:56.360
I'd like to see how he performs

00:05:04.639 --> 00:05:05.199
Hei Ba

00:05:05.879 --> 00:05:07.399
You asked for this yourself

00:05:08.639 --> 00:05:09.519
You want to die

00:05:09.800 --> 00:05:10.720
I'll grant your wish

00:05:21.839 --> 00:05:23.439
What's the status of the betting pool?

00:05:29.759 --> 00:05:31.480
Once they heard Hei Ba is challenging the Five Little Dragons

00:05:32.040 --> 00:05:33.360
it attracted a lot of bets

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:43.360
Hei Ba

00:05:43.720 --> 00:05:46.079
It seems I really have to thank you

00:05:46.439 --> 00:05:48.600
I didn't expect that besides seeking your own death

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.399
you'd also bring me an unexpected surprise

00:05:52.959 --> 00:05:54.319
Go adjust the odds

00:05:54.560 --> 00:05:55.720
You know what to do

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:19.920
Hey

00:06:20.680 --> 00:06:21.160
Hei Ba

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:23.720
Xishi, Sister Wu and Ball Boy Wei He are very mysterious

00:06:24.480 --> 00:06:26.240
I haven't figured out exactly who they are either

00:06:26.959 --> 00:06:27.759
Are you confident?

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:29.920
Don't worry

00:06:30.360 --> 00:06:31.399
That Ball Boy Wei He

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.000
has a history with me

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:34.199
I'm sorry

00:06:35.079 --> 00:06:36.160
I can't be of much help

00:06:36.959 --> 00:06:38.399
You've already helped me a lot

00:06:39.680 --> 00:06:40.600
Leave the rest to me

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:01.480
I've seen you play Snooker before.

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:03.160
But I'm sorry to say,

00:07:03.560 --> 00:07:05.959
Chinese Pool isn't like fussy Snooker.

00:07:06.639 --> 00:07:08.800
Chinese Pool is the realm of power shots.

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:09.360
Power

00:07:09.600 --> 00:07:10.800
is everything.

00:07:11.519 --> 00:07:12.720
Attack only, no defense.

00:07:14.480 --> 00:07:15.560
You haven't changed a bit.

00:07:15.959 --> 00:07:16.759
What did you say?

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.879
But your cue has certainly been upgraded.

00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:23.319
Chinese Pool does emphasize offense more.

00:07:23.600 --> 00:07:25.959
But power shots make the ball hard to control.

00:07:26.319 --> 00:07:28.519
Especially with a specially treated cue.

00:07:28.920 --> 00:07:30.399
Who exactly are you?

00:07:39.399 --> 00:07:40.600
By using brute force,

00:07:40.959 --> 00:07:42.879
you try to leave scratches on the cue ball,

00:07:43.279 --> 00:07:44.439
to affect your opponent's touch.

00:07:45.079 --> 00:07:47.000
It affects finesse players greatly.

00:07:47.759 --> 00:07:48.279
But you,

00:07:48.360 --> 00:07:49.839
you're better at solving problems with violence.

00:07:50.480 --> 00:07:52.160
So it affects you very little.

00:07:53.600 --> 00:07:55.399
I don't know what you're talking about.

00:07:56.120 --> 00:07:57.240
A normal cue

00:07:57.800 --> 00:07:59.240
can hardly affect the ball.

00:08:00.040 --> 00:08:02.160
So what did you add to the tip?

00:08:02.680 --> 00:08:03.639
Diamond dust?

00:08:06.160 --> 00:08:07.600
Do you have proof?

00:08:08.399 --> 00:08:10.920
Or are you just making excuses for losing?

00:08:12.199 --> 00:08:13.439
It doesn't matter if you don't admit it.

00:08:14.000 --> 00:08:15.439
Because I won't lose.

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:17.040
Let me teach you a lesson.

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.600
I do rely heavily on touch when I play.

00:08:25.519 --> 00:08:26.839
But power shots...

00:08:30.959 --> 00:08:32.440
I'm just as good at them.

00:08:36.759 --> 00:08:37.279
You are...

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.919
You are Captain Jack.

00:08:39.440 --> 00:08:40.320
When I beat you last time,

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:41.200
I intended to teach you

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:43.159
to balance power and control.

00:08:43.600 --> 00:08:44.960
I didn't expect you to be unrepentant.

00:08:45.399 --> 00:08:46.399
And even get worse.

00:08:47.519 --> 00:08:49.440
Stop acting all high and mighty.

00:08:49.919 --> 00:08:50.879
I lost to you last time

00:08:51.000 --> 00:08:52.320
because I lacked stamina.

00:08:52.759 --> 00:08:54.519
Causing my power to falter later on.

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:56.320
I'm not afraid to tell you,

00:08:56.919 --> 00:08:59.399
I am using a specially treated cue.

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:01.240
It changes the weight balance.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:02.320
Making my power shots

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.960
much easier to execute.

00:09:04.480 --> 00:09:05.159
This time,

00:09:05.559 --> 00:09:06.960
I won't run out of steam.

00:09:07.559 --> 00:09:09.240
I'm going to clear the table.

00:09:09.720 --> 00:09:11.480
I won't give you any chance.

00:09:11.879 --> 00:09:13.200
I'm taking back the victory

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:14.840
you stole from my hands.

00:09:29.519 --> 00:09:31.919
Why is Hei Ba so weak now?

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:33.639
He's not even struggling.

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:35.639
If he loses just like that,

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:37.039
that would be so embarrassing.

00:09:37.679 --> 00:09:39.320
I'm going to go see for myself.

00:09:39.879 --> 00:09:41.600
See how miserably he loses.

00:09:57.879 --> 00:09:58.519
Fake it.

00:09:59.200 --> 00:10:00.840
Let's see you keep faking.

00:10:01.519 --> 00:10:03.480
What is going on with Hei Ba?

00:10:04.840 --> 00:10:06.399
Is he going to lose the first game?

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.360
I'm going to win.

00:10:10.080 --> 00:10:12.000
Almost there.

00:10:19.559 --> 00:10:20.759
Let me teach you another lesson.

00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:22.240
A specially treated cue

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.120
does give your shots more power.

00:10:24.639 --> 00:10:25.759
But it also magnifies your weakness

00:10:26.399 --> 00:10:27.559
infinitely.